=====
Visitor Activity
=====

Visitor Activity is an app to track down source and data for requested urls and 
writes it to file.
Will be merged into core app consisting of handy tools in future.

Quick start
-----------

1. Add 'visitor_activity' to your installed apps

INSTALLED_APPS = (
    ...
    'visitor_activity.apps.VisitorActivityConfig',
)

2. Specify USER_ACTIVITY_LOG_FILENAME. Path to a logging file.

USER_ACTIVITY_LOG_FILENAME = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'visitor_activity.log')